d meeting deadlines it’s a real job and not just another group that i’m a part of this realworld experience is going to give me an advantage over my peers when i begin looking for an internship or job” college is an experience not just a degree “don’t let yourself get caught up in the academic life and don’t let the college life overtake you either you’re paying for the entire experience not just the degree but remember that you’re in college to position yourself to succeed in the real world” get to know your ra “i never thought i would become friends with my ra or ma once i got to know them i realized they make time for everything and everyone even though they’re just as busy as the rest of us my ra brandi taught me to relax and not stress about the little things” life at central account executive at central michigan life intramural football and basketball hall council member ​ ​​ fired up and focused cmichedu facebook icon twitter icon youtube icon instagram icon linkedin icon central michigan university •  s franklin st • mount pleasant mich 4 • 44 cmichedu rajat taneja quits microsoft for ea  latest news from the game development industry  develop your site will load in  seconds skip this  develop main menu home news features opinions in depth post mortem studio profiles jobs events magazine newsletters follow us facebook twitter linkedin google youtube rss feed subscribe to our newsletter about about us advertise contact us writers jem alexander joab gilroy leigh harris marie dealessandri sean cleaver newbay network audio media international bikebiz develop installation licensingbiz mcv uk mcv pacific mi pro music week pcr psneurope toynews tv tech global tvb europe esports mccormack  morrison doubleclick regenology sarsen comscore develop conference ukie tiga connection events gdc games press search rajat taneja quits microsoft for ea by craig chapple september rd  at am share share this article facebook twitter linkedin google email print former vp leaves after  years at computer giant rajat taneja has quit his role as corporate vp of commerce at microsoft and joined ea as global chief technology officerhe leaves his role as corporate vp at microsoft’s commerce division after  years working at the computer gianthe will now be responsible for driving critical technology decisions and investments for electronic arts on a global basis“gaming is at a technological confluence that is almost unprecedented where commerce online delivery of content and services and multiple engagement platforms are converging” said taneja “it’s an exciting time to join ea where they are clearly executing against a vision to lead the industry through this transition and deliver the best content to consumers”taneja’s previous work at microsoft included leading the division responsible for development and deployment of all commerce and transaction technologies across online services such as xbox live and windows phone he had also previously led the pc giant’s online digital advertising platforms and their first business online service offeringrajat is an exceptional addition to our executive leadership team at ea said ea ceo john riccitiello his experience building a worldclass online commerce and service platform will help ea continue our transformation into a leading provider of digital games and services tags ea microsoft online electronic arts john riccitiello rajat taneja please enable javascript to view the comments powered by disqus comments powered by disqus  prev next  related articles 4 industries and the legacy of the halo brand  licensingbiz july th  reports that microsoft layoffs will reach to over  july th  crosswires why is crossplay an issue june th  get the latest news sent to your inbox sign up to receive our email news updates and access to other online products and services follow us facebook twitter google linkedin rss job spotlight experienced game developer reach robotics technical game designer reach robotics more jobs most